{"id": "QmS9qJLkFRrFhbNXqindsoCjLYhQEYUNntKR4YNwHqZH8f", "title": "Bond bonuses for MIB holders", "body": "**Rationale:** \n\nBonds have for a long time had no use at all, so providing direct incentives for bond holders to purchase Mithril Cash will drastically improve utility of the token. Meanwhile, Bond Bonuses provide an alternative route to reducing the number of Mithril Bonds.\n\n**Expected Result:** \n\nBond Bonuses will attract buyers who have previously purchased Mithril Bonds.\n\n**Logic:**\n\nFor each 10 $MIC purchased by Bond holders, 1 Bond may be burned in exchange for 1 newly minted $MIC. Bond bonuses will be optional, and according to supply and demand we can afford to mint extra $MIC for bond holders as long as they are buying a larger amount of $MIC itself. Example is as follows:\n\nTom is a Mithril Bond holder. He buys 1000 $MIC through our contract, and agrees to burn 100 of his bonds. Tom is instantly sent 1,100 $MIC total, 1,000 of which came from the liquidity pool, and 100 of which was newly minted by the Bond Bonus contract.\n\nThis ratio of 1:10 persists with any size buy order. This means if Tom wanted to, he could buy 1 $MIC and burn 0.1 MIB in exchange for 1.1 $MIC.", "choices": ["Add bond bonuses", "Do nothing"], "start": 1622221200, "end": 1622480400, "snapshot": "12523971", "state": "closed", "author": "0x1a09Ce0614A53419850E107857ACb875DF00aF2E", "space": {"id": "mithcash2.eth", "name": "MITH Cash 2"}, "votes": 14, "votes_data": [{"id": "QmNuJYzJe3mgyvraeULxwC6GmWFoJSYSwWQbtwshgFiE4g", "voter": "0xa7804BC65158b02817874dC8b457C71F040E3945", "created": 1622395300, "choice": 2, "space": {"id": "mithcash2.eth"}}, {"id": "QmXZqBMCrdoXZMJgjaQDkHSXF6hL2fi6wKkUib6ADvrfzh", "voter": "0x4a21040B18Ba0e18B48Fb69233982756A67A0dcC", "created": 1622356556, "choice": 1, "space": {"id": "mithcash2.eth"}}, {"id": "QmQLwY431kfbyegMvJQQaVqYhYNXU77iEChoh8ymjM6n33", "voter": "0xcea51a7D0b68E77b733d3f76DB46e366EAD9470e", "created": 1622333237, "choice": 1,